2011-02-28T23:56:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/india-daybook-mukherjee-meets-industry-manufacturing-data.html
Finance Minister Pranab Mukherjee
will meet representatives from Indian industry after unveiling a
budget proposal yesterday designed to ease the impact of
inflation on lower-income earners by exempting more people from
paying taxes, while inviting foreign investment in
infrastructure and accelerating sales of state-owned assets.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Malavika Sharma in  New Delhi  at 
